  70:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c **** /*
  71:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  * Test the bits set in uxCurrentEventBits to see if the wait condition is met.
  72:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  * The wait condition is defined by xWaitForAllBits.  If xWaitForAllBits is
  73:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  * pdTRUE then the wait condition is met if all the bits set in uxBitsToWaitFor
  74:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  * are also set in uxCurrentEventBits.  If xWaitForAllBits is pdFALSE then the
  75:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  * wait condition is met if any of the bits set in uxBitsToWait for are also set
  76:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  * in uxCurrentEventBits.
  77:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/event_groups.c ****  */
